    <summary>Lightweight Windows RAM cleaner â€” 142KB static binary with system tray, hotkey, and auto-clean support.</summary>
    <description>RAMKeeper is a lightweight (142KB) portable Windows RAM cleaner that purges the standby/cached memory list via NtSetSystemInformation, immediately reclaiming memory without rebooting.

## Features

- **System tray app** â€” runs quietly in the background
- **Global hotkey** â€” Ctrl+Alt+R triggers an instant purge from anywhere
- **Auto-clean modes** â€” threshold-based (purge when free RAM drops below N%), interval-based (purge every N minutes), and idle-based (purge after N minutes of inactivity)
- **No runtime dependencies** â€” single static binary, no .NET, no MSVC redistributable
- **No ads, no telemetry** â€” MIT licensed, open source

## Notes

RAMKeeper requires administrator privileges because the standby memory purge needs SeProfileSingleProcessPrivilege.

This is a portable executable. Chocolatey installs it to the tools directory and creates a shim so `RAMKeeper` is available from any terminal.
    </description>
